{"id": "1264344936162263091", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "593627944979660800", "author_name": "gum1206", "author_bot": false, "content": "500沈澱啟靈一定是優先給限定的，順位一般就是泛用度、需高啟。\n另外4小強一定是先拉起來到60，滿3啟的，融災必備好用SR。\n第五隊，就是全60，技能全3，融1一定可以等級輾壓。", "timestamp": "2024-07-20T22:15:23.174000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1249274074593759293"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1264198022812667996", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
